                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17690628-61-victim584 t17690628-61-viclabel341"></join>, in the occupation of the prisoner, with intent to set on fire the dwelling houses of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17690628-61-victim586" type="victimName">
                           Miles 
                           Wells 
                        <interp inst="t17690628-61-victim586" type="surname" value="Wells"></interp>
