                     <interp inst="t17690628-61-person603" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The morning her house was on fire I looked in at the window of the shop about twenty minutes before seven; there was a basket seemingly to be used to carry greens in, some straw, and leaves of greens, and nothing else but a few old boards. I could see all over the shop.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17690628-61-person604">
                  Clement 
                  Scot 
               <interp inst="t17690628-61-person604" type="surname" value="Scot"></interp>
